Returns the number of megabytes used by a file, rounded to the nearest MB
Performs FP arithmetic (other than $(()) ) If the result is a whole number, a dot is appended at the end (FORTRAN compatibility) TODO: Invert default behaviour (most callers do not expect FT compatibility)
Creates a proper dependency string out of several inputs.
